data.text: @ACTHealth Hey Aboriginal and Torres Strait Islander families & friends  🖤❤️💛💚 the COVID-19 vaccines have over 3 MILLION adverse reports documented by the WORLD HEALTH ORGANISATION https://t.co/PwTGefR2ro database in less than a year. Even the CEO of Pfizer says the vaccines don't work. https://t.co/SuYoXDYMlV
@ACTHealth As if. Wasting our taxpayers money again with PC nonsense.

✅ No booking or Medicare card is required and it’s free.

More information at https://t.co/34BSS1kn6c

💪🏾 People aged 16+ should have a booster dose 3 months after their second dose. If this is your second or booster dose, please bring proof of your previous vaccinations if possible
✅ Young people (between 5-15 years) should have a parent or guardian present for their vaccination https://t.co/DS7BGRIcyR

We’ll be here from 10 to 3pm (last walk-ins at 2.30pm). There will be kids activities and entertainment, as well as light refreshments.
✅ Aboriginal and Torres Strait Islander people aged 5+ can come along and get vaccinated. https://t.co/AIFqSMOttQ
